oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Miss Gene Beasley, from the Nashville Times, 1940
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A published photo from the Nashville Times (1940), showing Miss Gene Beasley as a snow skier; the landscape scenery shows a heavy snow in Nashville. Forms part of the Nashville Times newspaper collection. 1 digital photo.
